page.title: 19Credits
page.content: The children of class 1D in St. Wilfrid's School would like to thank the following people for the help given to them in the collecting of information for this project; Mr.J. Attrill - Farmer (Dean Farm). Mrs.R. Blake - Steephill Cove. Mr.A. Butler - Local Fisherman. Mr.R. Dignan - Father of Michael in class 1C. Miss R. Howe - Retired Teacher who still takes an active part in all community activities. Mr. R. McInnes- Author and father of Fiona in class 1C. Mr. H. Noyes - Son of the poet Alfred Noyes. Mr. P. Wright - Niton Marine Radio Station. A Typical Day in my Life was compiled by the class group.
